Invocation Name: gettysburg guide
des:
A guide to Gettysburg, Pennsylvania; providing an overview and history of the city, as well as places to visit. This skill can help you get around town to see what is worth seeing, and where you can stop to relax or grab a bite to eat.

Plan a day out by learning about what attractions there are within Gettysburg:
 • What are the top five things to do in Gettysburg?
 • Where can we get something to eat?
 • How is the weather looking for today?

Learn about the history of the town and the American Civil War that so many know the town for today:
 • Tell me something interesting about the American Civil War.
 • I want to know more about the battle of Gettysburg.
 • Tell me about someone famous from Gettysburg.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
